22. Git Troubleshooting (SRE Section)

Recover deleted commit:

git reflog
git reset --hard <commit>

Undo bad merge:

git reset --hard HEAD~1

Restore deleted file:

git checkout <commit> -- file.txt

Find bug introduction commit:

git bisect
23. Git Best Practices for SRE

Branches: feature/*, bugfix/*, hotfix/*

Commit messages:

fix: memory leak
feat: retry logic
docs: update README

Avoid force pushes on shared branches

Use pull requests for review

Small, logical commits

24. Production Workflow Example
git checkout -b fix-memory-leak
git add .
git commit -m "fix: memory leak in worker"
git push origin fix-memory-leak

Workflow:

Create branch → Implement → Commit → Push → PR → Review → Merge → Deploy

